00:24:31.060 --> 00:24:32.490 align:middle line:90%
So here's what happened.

00:24:32.490 --> 00:24:36.320 align:middle line:84%
Randy Jirtle, a scientist
at Duke University,

00:24:36.320 --> 00:24:40.160 align:middle line:84%
